			<ns0:name>mseaborn@chromium.org</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/mseaborn@chromium.org/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">I am splitting this out from issue 1796.  native_client/src/shared/imc/osx/nacl_imc.cc contains two sets of workaround code:

 1) Code using ControlBlock, which is #if'd out.
 2) A recvmsg() retry loop, using kRecvMsgRetries.  If this is working around the kernel bug described in issue 1796, it's not needed, but it wouldn't work reliably even if it were needed.

Both of these can be removed.
